      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so i was just cleaning my ears with a cotton swab and i heard this weird loud pop in my left ear. now it's like... totally silent on that side. it's kind of annoying but i feel fine otherwise. is this just like tinnitus or maybe just some wax buildup? i'm in oslo right now",
