      "content": "idk i dont really want to go to the doctor if i can help it, it's such a hassle and i have work tomorrow. its not like i'm in pain or anything, just quiet. do u think i could just try some ear drops or maybe use a tea tree oil thing to clear it out? i feel like it's probably just some pressure issue that'll settle down overnight.",
