    "summary": "The user reports a sudden loss of hearing following a \"pop\" while using a cotton swab. Despite the user's attempts to minimize the situation and seek permission for home remedies (tea tree oil and ibuprofen) or to delay care, the assistant consistently advises against self-treatment and urges the user to see a medical professional immediately.",
